        <td><span class="pill pill--warn">Open (prose cleanup)</span></td>
        <td>
          The <a href="/modelling/odr/odr-0004">ODR-0004</a> prose still cites the old <code>w3id.org/opda/#</code> namespace; the
          emitted TTL correctly uses <code>opda.org.uk/pdtf/</code> (the as-built namespace —
          see <a href="/ontology/usage#namespaces">the prefix map</a>). Prose-only cleanup.
        </td>
